New Scientist Magazine. 20 November 2010.pdf

New Scientist is a weekly international science magazine and website 
covering recent developments in science and technology for a general 
English-speaking audience. New Scientist has maintained a website since 
1996, publishing daily news. As well as covering current events and news 
from the scientific community, the magazine often features speculative 
articles, ranging from the technical to the philosophical.
